iversity-of-technology-and-management-bhubaneswar-campus-53057/questions"><span>Q&amp;A<!-- --> </span></a></li><li class=""><a class=" listItem ripple dark" title="Centurion University Bhubaneswar Scholarships" href="https://www.shiksha.com/college/centurion-university-of-technology-and-management-bhubaneswar-campus-53057/scholarships"><span>Scholarships<!-- --> </span></a></li><li class=""><a class=" listItem ripple dark" title="Centurion University Bhubaneswar News &amp; Articles" href="https://www.shiksha.com/college/centurion-university-of-technology-and-management-bhubaneswar-campus-53057/news-articles"><span>News<!-- --> </span></a></li><li class="d13b89" style="width: 85px; transform: translateX(8px);"></li></ul><div class="e0a4"><div class="c3b3"><div class="_22ce _0cfb"><img loading="lazy" class="_6d97 _6e6d _9016" src="./cutmhome_files/darkClock.svg" alt="Dark Clock Icon"><span class="_0a9d _1452"> <!-- -->Last updated on<!-- --> <b>5 Jan '24</b></span></div></div></div><section class="de91 " id="iulp_lhs_container"><div class="paper-card boxShadow baac"><div class="e3e7  a694 h2"><div class="b3ca"><i class="uilpIcon whatsNew"></i></div><h2 class="_2b31"><div class="fe79">Centurion University Bhubaneswar </div><div class="_6a22 ">What’s new?</div></h2></div><div class="_859c"><div class="wikiContents _021e collapsed ca53 _5333  blueGradient wikiIntro disabledReadmore c225" style="max-height:unset"><div><div class="faq__according-wrapper"><div><p>GATE 2024 exam will be conducted between <strong>Feb 3, 2024</strong> and <strong>Feb 11, 2024</strong>.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div role="group" aria-roledescription="carousel" aria-live="polite" class="_528a "><div class="_0b93" aria-label="latestArticles"><div class="_0f11 _5c23 " style="transform:translateX(-0px);transition:transform 0.25s ease-in-out" tabindex="0"><div class="_003c" data-index="1"><div class="_1cb3"><span>Dec 21, 2023<!-- --> </span></div><div class="d2cd">Centurion University Bhubaneswar Rankings 2023: Busine...<a class="_0472 ripple dark" href="https://www.shiksha.com/business-management-studies/articles/centurion-university-bhubaneswar-rankings-2023-business-today-blogId-147393">Read More</a><div class="_05ef">Centurion University Bhubaneswar Rankings 2023: Business Today</div></div></div><div class="_003c" data-index="2"><div class="_1cb3"><span>Dec 21, 2023<!-- --> </span></div><div class="d2cd">Centurion University Rankings 2023: Times Higher Educa...<a class="_0472 ripple dark" href="https://www.shiksha.com/business-management-studies/articles/centurion-university-rankings-2023-times-higher-education-blogId-147391">Read More</a><div class="_05ef">Centurion University Rankings 2023: Times Higher Education</div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="_8da5"><div class="_8efd _0ead collapsed "><div class="_2b9a _147f"><div class="ca16"><div><div class="d3c6">Centurion University Bhubaneswar <!-- -->Overview</div><span class="_559d">Table of content</span></div><img loading="lazy" class="_377d  undefined  b4e9 _6e6d" src="./cutmhome_files/chevron-up.svg" alt="Accordion Icon V3"></div></div><div class="_1003 _7e88 _5661"><ul class="_1b4e97 newTocListV2  "><li class="" data-scrol="ovp_section_highlights">Centurion University Bhubaneswar Highlights 2024</li><li class="" data-scrol="ovp_section_popular_courses">Centurion University Bhubaneswar Popular Programmes 2024</li><li class="" data-scrol="ovp_section_admission_dates">Centurion University Bhubaneswa Admission Dates 2024</li><li class="" data-scrol="ovp_section_placements">Centurion University Bhubaneswar Placements 2024</li><li class="" data-scrol="ovp_section_fees_and_eligibility">Centurion University Bhubaneswar Courses and Fees 2024</li><li class="" data-scrol="ovp_section_reviews">Centurion University Bhubaneswar Student Reviews</li><li class="" data-scrol="ovp_section_rankings">Centurion University Bhubaneswar Rankings 2024</li><li class="" data-scrol="ovp_section_scholarships">Centurion University Bhubaneswar Scholarships 2024</li><li class="" data-scrol="ovp_section_infrastructure">Centurion University Bhubaneswar Infrastructure</li><li class="" data-scrol="ovp_section_notable_alumni">Centurion University Bhubaneswar USPs</li><li class="" data-scrol="ovp_section_affiliated_colleges/departments">Centurion University Bhubaneswar Departments</li><li class="" data-scrol="ovp_section_fAQs">Centurion University Bhubaneswar FAQs</li></ul></div></div></div><div class="paper-card spacingVariation"><div class="a2ee"><div class="_8efd _57fd bb73 _48ca expanded " id="ovp_section_highlights"><div class="_2b9a _9b5a caaf"><div class="ca16"><div class=""><div class="e3e7  bdde h2"><h2 class="_2b31"><div class="_6a22 ">Centurion University Bhubaneswar Highlights 2024</div></h2></div></div><img loading="lazy" class="_377d _7ef0 undefined  b4e9 _6e6d" src="./cutmhome_files/chevron-up.svg" alt="Accordion Icon V3"></div></div><div class="_1003  _58f5"><div class="b120"><div class="wikiContents _021e collapsed ca53 _5333 a78b    _0443" style="content-visibility:auto;contain-intrinsic-size:auto 180px;--maxHeightOfBlock:180px"><div><div class="faq__according-wrapper"><div><p>Established in 2005, Centurion University of Technology and Management (CUTM) is a multi-sector, private university located in Odisha, India. Accredited with NAAC with ‘A’ grade, the main campus of CUTM is located at Paralakhemundi (Gajapati district). Centurion University has other campuses located in <strong>Bhubaneswar</strong> and Visakhapatnam (or Vizianagaram) along with three regional campuses located in Rayagarh, Balangir (or Bolangir) and Balasore.</p>
<p>Spread over 40 acres of land in the foothill of Barunei hills, near Jatni town, the Bhubaneswar campus of Centurion University of Technology and Management (CUTM) is located adjacent to NISER, IIT, AIIMS and Xavier University. Centurion University Bhubaneswar offers over 90+ courses across various fields such as Engineering, Management, Science, Mass Communication and Media, Design, Hotel Management and Pharmacy among various others. Mentioned below are a few highlights around Centurion University Bhubaneswar:</p>
<table style="width: 1135px; height: 223px;">
<tbody>
<tr style="height: 29px;">
<th style="width: 530.469px; height: 29px;">
<p>Particulars</p>
</th>
<th style="width: 569.531px; height: 29px;">
<p>Statistics</p>
</th>
</tr>
<tr style="height: 29px;">
<td style="width: 530.469px; height: 29px;">
<p>Year of establishment</p>
</td>
<td style="width: 569.531px; height: 29px;">
<p>2005 (main campus)</p>
