</table></div></div></div><div class="ad0e"></div><span class="_5ee4">Read more<!-- --> </span></div></div><div class="_0637"><div class="_9e70"><div class="d5f9"><div><img loading="lazy" class="_1752 _6e6d _22c3" src="./cutmhome_files/qna.svg" alt="Q&amp;A Icon"></div><div class="_5977"><h5>Commonly asked questions <div>On <!-- -->Highlights</div></h5></div></div><div id="sectional-faqs-0" class="_6e6a sectional-faqs"><p id="0::25943" class="_5543 listener" style="animation-delay:0s"><strong class="flx-box"> <span>Q: &nbsp;</span> <span>What is unique about Centurion University of Technology and Management, Bhubaneswar?</span></strong></p><div class="ff6c"><div class="wikiContents"><div class="_3063"> <span> A:&nbsp; </span> <div> *Outcome-Based Education: CUTM focuses on outcome-based education, emphasizing practical skills and industry relevance. The curriculum is designed to bridge the gap between academia and industry requirements, ensuring that students are well-prepared for their future careers. *Socially Oriented Approach: One of the distinctive features of CUTM is its commitment to social responsibility. The university actively engages in various social development initiatives and has established a dedicated social outreach programme called "Gram Tarang. " Through this programme, CUTM strives to empower rural communities, promote entrepreneurship, and create sustainable livelihood opportunities. *Industry Partnerships: CUTM has strong industry partnerships and collaborations. It works closely with leading companies and organizations to provide students with internships, industry projects, and exposure to real-world challenges. This helps students gain practical experience and enhances their employability. *Skill Development Centers: CUTM has Skill Development Centers that offer training programs in areas such as automotive, construction, hospitality, agriculture, healthcare, and more. These centers provide students with hands-on learning opportunities and help develop industry-specific skills.</div></div></div><a class="e21b" href="https://ask.shiksha.com/what-is-unique-about-centurion-university-of-technology-and-management-bhubaneswar-qna-7444035"> <!-- -->View Other Answers<!-- --> <i class="_6c18 d30c"></i></a></div><p id="0::348205" class="_5543 listener" style="animation-delay:0s"><strong class="flx-box"> <span>Q: &nbsp;</span> <span>Is Centurion University of Technology and Management, Bhubaneswar Campus a private or government institute? </span></strong></p><div class="ff6c"><div class="wikiContents"><div class="_3063"> <span> A:&nbsp; </span> <div> <p>The Centurion University of Technology and Management, Bhubaneswar Campus is a private university. It is located on the Barunei hills. The university offers over 100 courses and is known for its focus on skills, entrepreneurship, and sustainable innovations. It provides a range of programs including graduate, postgraduate, doctoral, diploma, and certificate courses.&nbsp;</p></div></div></div></div><p id="0::348207" class="_5543 listener" style="animation-delay:0s"><strong class="flx-box"> <span>Q: &nbsp;</span> <span>What is Centurion University of Technology and Management, Bhubaneswar Campus famous for? </span></strong></p><div class="ff6c"><div class="wikiContents"><div class="_3063"> <span> A:&nbsp; </span> <div> <p>The Centurion University of Technology and Management in Bhubaneswar, Odisha, is famous for its unique approach to education and its commitment to skill development, entrepreneurship, and sustainable innovations. The university offers a blend of traditional, applied, and action learning to develop productive citizens. Centurion University is also known for its School of Vocational Training, which is pioneering the concept of vocational training in India.&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p></div></div></div></div><p id="0::365967" class="_5543 listener" style="animation-delay:0s"><strong class="flx-box"> <span>Q: &nbsp;</span> <span>How is the college life at Centurion University of Technology and Management, Bhubaneswar?</span></strong></p><div class="ff6c"><div class="wikiContents"><div class="_3063"> <span> A:&nbsp; </span> <div> Campus Environment: CUTM boasts a spacious and well-equipped campus that creates a conducive learning environment. With modern infrastructure, well-designed classrooms, libraries, and recreational spaces, the campus provides students with everything they need for their academic and extracurricular pursuits. Academic Programs: CUTM offers a diverse range of academic programs spanning various disciplines, including engineering, management, agriculture, applied sciences, and more. The curriculum is carefully designed to strike a balance between theoretical knowledge and practical skills, ensuring that students develop a strong academic foundation. Faculty and Staff: The faculty members at CUTM are highly dedicated, knowledgeable, and supportive. They play a crucial role in guiding students, conducting engaging classes, and providing mentorship. The staff members are also available to assist students with administrative and logistical matters, creating a supportive environment. Student Activities and Clubs: CUTM encourages student engagement through a wide range of clubs, student organizations, and extracurricular activities. Cultural events, sports competitions, technical competitions, and social initiatives provide students with ample opportunities for personal growth, skill development, and fostering long-lasting friendships. Industry Exposure and Internships: CUTM places a strong emphasis on industry-oriented education. The university collaborates with industries and organizations to offer internships, industrial visits, guest lectures, and workshops. These experiences provide students with practical exposure to the corporate world, bridging the gap between academia and the professional sphere. Cultural and Sports Events: Throughout the year, CUTM organizes captivating cultural and sports events, infusing the campus with a lively and vibrant atmosphere. Students can showcase their talents in music, dance, drama, and sports through competitions, festivals, and annual gatherings. These events promote camaraderie and celebrate the diverse student community. Social Initiatives and Community Service: CUTM instills a sense of social responsibility and community engagement in its students. Active participation in community service initiatives, volunteering activities, and social awareness campaigns allows students to contribute positively to society and develop a strong sense of social consciousness. </div></div></div><a class="e21b" href="https://ask.shiksha.com/how-is-the-college-life-at-centurion-university-of-technology-and-management-bhubaneswar-qna-7444055"> <!-- -->View Other Answers<!-- --> <i class="_6c18 d30c"></i></a></div><p id="0::365969" class="_5543 listener" style="animation-delay:0s"><strong class="flx-box"> <span>Q: &nbsp;</span> <span>What are the top courses offered at Centurion University of Technology and Management, Bhubaneswar?</span></strong></p><div class="ff6c"><div class="wikiContents"><div class="_3063"> <span> A:&nbsp; </span> <div> <p>The top courses offered at Centurion University of Technology and Management, Bhubaneswar include:<br>Bachelor of Technology (B.Tech)<br>Bachelor of Business Administration (BBA)<br>Master of Science (M.Sc)<br>Bachelor of Science (B.Sc)<br>Master of Business Administration (MBA)<br>Ph.D.<br>Polytechnic<br>The university offers a wide range of courses at various levels, including diploma, undergraduate, postgraduate, and doctoral programs. Some of the popular courses at the undergraduate level are B.Tech, BBA, and B.Sc, while at the postgraduate level, M.Sc and MBA are preferred choices. The university also offers a Ph.D. program for those interested in pursuing research and advanced studies.</p></div></div></div><a class="e21b" href="https://ask.shiksha.com/what-are-the-top-courses-offered-at-centurion-university-of-technology-and-management-bhubaneswar-qna-7444067"> <!-- -->View Other Answers<!-- --> <i class="_6c18 d30c"></i></a></div><p id="0::1116657" class="_5543 listener" style="animation-delay:0s"><strong class="flx-box"> <span>Q: &nbsp;</span> <span>How can I get direct admission in MCA at Centurion University? </span></strong></p><div class="ff6c"><div class="wikiContents"><div class="_3063"> <span> A:&nbsp; </span> <div> <p>MCA Admission Criteria at Centurion University Bhubaneswar-</p><ul><li>Major criteria: JEE Mains/OJEE score/rank and graduation with 50%</li><li>Course duration: 2 years full-time</li><li>Tuition fee: INR 1.9 lakh</li><li>Eligibility: Bachelor's degree in Computer Science Engineering or equivalent degree, or B.Sc./B.Com./B.A. with Mathematics at 10+2 or graduation level (with additional bridge courses)</li></ul></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="_50f3 multipleTableContainer"></div></div></div></div></div><section class="_1248 boxShadow undefined" id="ovp_section_popular_courses"><div class="e3e7  a694 h2"><h2 class="_2b31"><div class="_6a22 ">Centurion University Bhubaneswar Popular Programmes 2024</div></h2></div><div class=""><div class="_7911 base_course_tuple "><div class="_1822 _0fc7  _80b2" id="tuple_26"><div class="_8165"><div class="_2cd2"><div class="_6255"><div class="cd76"><div class="_9be9"></div><div class="_557e"><div class="c8ff"><a class="ripple dark" href="https://www.shiksha.com/college/centurion-university-of-technology-and-management-bhubaneswar-campus-53057/courses/bsc-bc"><h3 title="Centurion University Bhubaneswar B.Sc." class="f7cc">B.Sc.</h3></a></div><div class="edfa"><span class="c877"><a title="20 courses in Centurion University Bhubaneswar" class="_9865 f7cc ripple dark" href="https://www.shiksha.com/college/centurion-university-of-technology-and-management-bhubaneswar-campus-53057/courses/bsc-bc">20 Courses</a><a class="_68c4 ripple dark" href="https://www.shiksha.com/college/centu