war-campus-53057/courses/msc-bc"><h3 title="Centurion University Bhubaneswar M.Sc." class="f7cc">M.Sc.</h3></a></div><div class="edfa"><span class="c877"><a title="16 courses in Centurion University Bhubaneswar" class="_9865 f7cc ripple dark" href="https://www.shiksha.com/college/centurion-university-of-technology-and-management-bhubaneswar-campus-53057/courses/msc-bc">16 Courses</a><a class="_68c4 ripple dark" href="https://www.shiksha.com/college/centurion-university-of-technology-and-management-bhubaneswar-campus-53057/reviews?bc=100"><img loading="lazy" class="_1bbb _6e6d _9016" src="./cutmhome_files/star.svg" alt="Star Icon"><span>4.4</span></a></span><span>2 - 5 years</span></div></div></div></div><button data-courseid="480947" data-trackid="6053" aria-label="Save Button" role="button" id="shrt_480947" class="_681c dfb4 pwa-shrtlst-ico tupleShortlistButton shrt_480947"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M14.25 15.75L9 12L3.75 15.75V3.75C3.75 3.35218 3.90804 2.97064 4.18934 2.68934C4.47064 2.40804 4.85218 2.25 5.25 2.25H12.75C13.1478 2.25 13.5294 2.40804 13.8107 2.68934C14.092 2.97064 14.25 3.35218 14.25 3.75V15.75Z" stroke="#2F1238" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg><span style="display:none"></span></button></div><div class="_0a31"><div class="cd4f _5c64 contentColumn_3"><div class="_77ff"><label class="abce">Exams Accepted</label><div class="dcfd undefined"><ul class="_0954"><li class=""><a title="CUEE" class="aace ripple dark" href="https://www.shiksha.com/engineering/cuee-exam">CUEE</a></li><li class="_11a2"><a title="CBSE 12th" class="aace _555b ripple dark" href="https://www.shiksha.com/boards/cbse-12th-board">CBSE 12th</a></li><li class="_11a2"><a title="Odisha CHSE" class="aace _555b ripple dark" href="https://www.shiksha.com/boards/odisha-chse-board">Odisha CHSE</a></li><li class="_151e"><span> <!-- -->+<!-- -->2<!-- --> </span></li></ul><