/cutmhome_files/star.svg" alt="Star Icon"><span>4.1</span></a></span><span>3 years</span></div></div></div></div><button data-courseid="480881" data-trackid="6053" aria-label="Save Button" role="button" id="shrt_480881" class="_681c dfb4 pwa-shrtlst-ico tupleShortlistButton shrt_480881"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 18 18" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M14.25 15.75L9 12L3.75 15.75V3.75C3.75 3.35218 3.90804 2.97064 4.18934 2.68934C4.47064 2.40804 4.85218 2.25 5.25 2.25H12.75C13.1478 2.25 13.5294 2.40804 13.8107 2.68934C14.092 2.97064 14.25 3.35218 14.25 3.75V15.75Z" stroke="#2F1238" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></svg><span style="display:none"></span></button></div><div class="_0a31"><div class="cd4f _5c64 contentColumn_3"><div class="_77ff"><label class="abce">Exams Accepted</label><div class="dcfd undefined"><ul class="_0954"><li class=""><a title="CUEE" class="aace ripple dark" href="https://www.shiksha.com/engineering/cuee-exam">CUEE</a></li></ul></div></div><div class="_77ff"><label class="abce">Total Tuition Fees</label><div class="dcfd f860">₹<!-- -->1.89 L<div><a id="getFeeDtl_480881" class="getFeesDetails_link fee_lftbtn getFeeDtl_480881" data-courseid="480881" data-trackid="8491" title="Get Fees Details of After 10th Diploma" data-feedtls="data-fees">Get Fee Details</a></div></div></div><div class="_77ff"><label class="abce">Median Salary</label><div class="dcfd" title="Centurion University Bhubaneswar  Placement"><span class="f393">– / –</span></div></div></div><div class="_54ea _362d"><div class="ebe3"><button class="b41b dfb4 _2782"><img loading="lazy" class="aa17 _6e6d d337" src="./cutmhome_files/compare.svg" alt="Compare Icon">Compare</button><button data-courseid="480881" data-trackid="6055" id="brchr_480881" class="dd41 dfb4 _2782 ctp-btn ctpBro-btn rippleefect tupleBrochureButton brchr_480881"><img loading="lazy" class="c9c7 _6e6d d337" src="./cutmhome_files/downloadIcon.svg" alt="Download Icon">Brochure</button></div></div></div></div></div></div><a class="_59a5 _5a11  ripple dark" href="https://www.shiksha.com/college/centurion-university-of-technology-and-management-bhubaneswar-campus-53057/courses"><div class="b952 _9857 primaryButton" role="button"><span class="d9de _9c85">View All 18 Courses</span><img loading="lazy" class="ffdf _6e6d d337" src="./cutmhome_files/RightArrow.svg" alt="Right Arrow Icon"></div></a><div class="_617a"><div class="_9e70"><div class="d5f9"><div><img loading="lazy" class="_1752 _6e6d _22c3" src="./cutmhome_files/qna.svg" alt="Q&amp;A Icon"></div><div class="_5977"><h5>Commonly asked questions <div>On <!-- -->Popular Programs</div></h5></div></div><div id="sectional-faqs-0" class="_6e6a sectional-faqs"><p id="0::348259" class="_5543 listener" style="animation-delay:0s"><strong class="flx-box"> <span>Q: &nbsp;</span> <span>What is the fee for various courses offered by Centurion University of Technology and Management, Bhubaneswar Campus? </span></strong></p><div class="ff6c"><div class="wikiContents"><div class="_3063"> <span> A:&nbsp; </span> <div> <p>The fee for various courses offered by Centurion University of Technology and Management, Bhubaneswar Campus:&nbsp;</p><p>BBA: Rs 66,000 per year</p><p>B.Tech: Rs 1.42 Lacs per year</p><p>M.Sc: Rs 80,000 per year</p><p>MBA: Rs 7.5 Lacs per year</p><p>M.Tech: Rs 78,750 per year</p><p>Polytechnic: Rs 52,500 per year</p><p>BA: Rs 1,05,000</p><p>Diploma in engineering: Rs 1,53,750</p><p>BCA: Rs 70,000 per year</p></div></div></div></div><p id="0::348261" class="_5543 listener" style="animation-delay:0s"><strong class="flx-box"> <span>Q: &nbsp;</span> <span>What are the courses offered at Centurion University of Technology and Management, Bhubaneswar Campus? </span></strong></p><div class="ff6c"><div class="wikiContents"><div class="_3063"> <span> A:&nbsp; </span> <div> <p>Centurion University of Technology and Management, Bhubaneswar offers a wide range of courses across various disciplines. Some of the courses available at the Bhubaneswar campus include BBA, B.Tech, M.Sc, MBA, M.Tech, Polytechnic, BA, Diploma in Engineering, BCA, commerce, pharmacy, agriculture management, medical, paramedical and computer applications.&nbsp;</p></div></div></div></div><p id="0::348263" class="_5543 listener" style="animation-delay:0s"><strong class="flx-box"> <span>Q: &nbsp;</span> <span>Is Centurion University of Technology and Management, Bhubaneswar Campus good for engineering? </span></strong></p><div class="ff6c"><div class="wikiContents"><div class="_3063"> <span> A:&nbsp; </span> <div> <div>Centurion University of Technology and Management, Bhubaneswar is a reputed educational institution offering a wide range of engineering courses. It is&nbsp;highly regarded for its&nbsp;engineering programs and industry collaborations.&nbsp;The university's hands-on approach to learning, strong links with industry and commitment to skills development make it a preferred choice for engineering aspirants.&nbsp;</div></div></div></div></div><p id="0::348265" class="_5543 listener" style="animation-delay:0s"><strong class="flx-box"> <span>Q: &nbsp;</span> <span>Which is the top course at Centurion University of Technology and Management, Bhubaneswar Campus? </span></strong></p><div class="ff6c"><div class="wikiContents"><div class="_3063"> <span> A:&nbsp; </span> <div> <div>Centurion University of Technology and Management, Bhubaneswar is a reputed educational institution offering a wide range of courses. The university is a top MBA college in Bhubaneshwar, Odisha. The national ranking framework ranked Centurion University Technology and Management number one for MBA. Some Popular courses from the university include B.Tech, MBBS, ME/M. Tech, B.Sc, BA, B.Com, etc.</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><div><div class="dfp-wraper"><div class="dfp-add"><div class="dfp-f-h" style="height: 76px; width: 600px; background: rgb(238, 238, 238);"></div></div></div><div class="dfp-wraper"><div class="dfp-add"><div class="dfp-f-h" style="height: 76px; width: 600px; background: rgb(238, 238, 238);"></div></div></div></div><div id="ovp_section_admission_dates"><section class="_1248 boxShadow" id="ovp_section_admission_dates"><div class="e3e7  a694 h2"><h2 class="_2b31"><div class="_6a22 ">Centurion University Bhubaneswa Admission Dates 2024</div></h2></div><div class=""><div class="_745f"><div class="_8efd _57fd ed37 _48ca expanded "><div class="_2b9a _9b5a _5127"><div class="ca16"><div class="_4b04"><h4>B.Sc. Admissions 2024</h4><div class="d950"><span>20 Courses</span><span class="dot"></span><span>2 years-5 years</span></div></div><img loading="lazy" class="_377d _7ef0 undefined  b4e9 _6e6d" src="./cutmhome_files/chevron-up.svg" alt="Accordion Icon V3"></div></div><div class="_1003  _58f5"><span class="a5a8 _2678"><img loading="lazy" class="_2b75 _6e6d d337" src="./cutmhome_files/check-circleV2.svg" alt="Check Circle Icon V2"><span>Eligibility</span></span><ul class="_45da"><li>10+2 with 50% aggregate</li><li><div>Accepting Exams: <strong>CBSE 12th, Odisha CHSE, CUEE</strong> </div></li></ul><div class="d4f1"><span class="c9a6 _2678"><img loading="lazy" class="_454c _6e6d d337" src="./cutmhome_files/calendar.svg" alt="Calendar Icon"><span>Important dates</span></span><span><button data-courseid="53057" data-trackid="8727" id="brchr_53057" class="c4a1 dfb4 b60e tupleBrochureButton brchr_53057">Download dates<img loading="lazy" class="c9c7 _6e6d d337" src="./cutmhome_files/dowloadblue.svg" alt="Blue Download Icon"></button></span></div><div class="_50f3 multipleTableContainer"><div><table id="dateWithExamsPdf_26" class="table _1708 d00e d8b0"><thead><tr><th class="fcc1">Dates</th><th class="fcc1">Events</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr class=""><td><div class="_3ad4">2 Dec '23 - 25 Aug '24</div></td><td><span class="_19b8"><span>CUEE 2024 Application Form</span><span class="_773d">Ongoing<!-- --> </span></span></td></tr><tr class=""><td><div class="_3ad4">30 Dec '23 - 30 Aug '24</div></td><td><span class="_19b8"><span>CUEE 2024 Exam Date</span><span class="_773d">Ongoing<!-- --> </span></span></td></tr></tbody></table></div></div></div></div><div class="_8efd _57fd ed37 _48ca collapsed "><div class="_2b9a _9b5a _5127"><div class="ca16"><div class="_4b04"><h4>B.E. / B.Tech Admissions 2024</h4><div class="d950"><span>8 Courses</span><span class="dot"></span><span>4 years</span></div></div><img loading="lazy" class="_377d  undefined  b4e9 _6e6d" src="./cutmhome_files/chevron-up.svg" alt="Accordion Icon V3"></div></div><div class="_1003 _7e88 _58f5"><span class="a5a8 _2678"><img loading="lazy" class="_2b75 _6e6d d337" src="./cutmhome_files/check-circleV2.svg" alt="Check Circle Icon V2"><span>Eligibility</span></span><ul class="_45da"><li>10+2 with 50% aggregate</li><li><div>Accepting Exams: <strong>CUEE, JEE Main</strong> </div></li></ul><div class="d4f1"><span class="c9a6 _2678"><img loading="lazy" class="_454c _6e6d d337" src="./cutmhome_files/calendar.svg" alt="Calendar Icon"><span>Important dates</span></span><span><button data-courseid="53057" data-trackid="8727" id="brchr_53057" class="c4a1 dfb4 b60e tupleBrochureButton brchr_53057">Download dates<img loading="lazy" class="c9c7 _6e6d d337" src="./cutmhome_files/dowloadblue.svg" alt="Blue Download Icon"></button></span></div><div class="_50f3 multipleTableContainer"><div><table id="dateWithExamsPdf_10" class="table _1708 d00e d8b0"><thead><tr><th class="fcc1">Dates</th><th class="fcc1">Events</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr class=""><td><div class="_3ad4">Jan '24</div></td><td><span class="_19b8"><span>JEE Main 2024 Admit Card</span><span class="_73a6">Tentative<!-- --> </span></span></td></tr><tr class=""><td><div class="_3ad4">24 Jan '24 - 1 Feb '24</div></td><td><span class="_19b8"><span>JEE Main 2024 Exam Date Session 1</span></span></td></tr><tr class=""><td><div class="_3ad4">12 Feb '24</div></td><td><span class="_19b8"><span>JEE Main 2024 Result Session 1</span></span></td></tr></tbody></table></div></div></div></div><div class="_8efd _57fd ed37 _48ca collapsed "><div class="_2b9a _9b5a _5127"><div class="ca16"><div class="_4b04"><h4>M.Sc. Admissions 2024</h4><div class="d950"><span>16 Courses</span><span class="dot"></span><span>2 years-5 years</span></div></div><img loading="lazy" class="_377d  undefined  b4e9 _6e6d" src="./cutmhome_files/chevron-up.svg" alt="Accordion Icon V3"></div></div><div class="_1003 _7e88 _58f5"><span class="a5a8 _2678"><img loading="lazy" class="_2b75 _6e6d d337" src="./cutmhome_files/check-circleV2.svg" alt="Check Circle Icon V2"><span>Eligibility</span></span><ul class="_45da"><li>Undergraduate Degree with 40% aggregate</li><li>10+2 with 50% aggregate</li><li><div>Accepting Exams: <strong>CUEE, CBSE 12th, Odisha CHSE</strong> </div></li></ul><div class="d4f1"><span class="c9a6 _2678"><img loading="lazy" class="_454c _6e6d d337" src="./cutmhome_files/calendar.svg" alt="Calendar Icon"><span>Important dates</span></span><span><button data-courseid="53057" data-trackid="8727" id="brchr_53057" class="c4a1 dfb4 b60e tupleBrochureButton brchr_53057">Download dates<img loading="lazy" class="c9c7 _6e6d d337" src="./cutmhome_files/dowloadblue.svg" alt="Blue Download Icon"></button></span></div><div class="_50f3 multipleTableContainer"><div><table id="dateWithExamsPdf_100" class="table _1708 d00e d8b0"><thead><tr><th class="fcc1">Dates</th><th class="fcc1">Events</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr class=""><td><div class="_3ad4">26 Dec '23 - 24 Jan '24</div></td><td><span class="_19b8"><span>CUET PG 2024 Application Process</span><span class="_773d">Ongoing<!-- --> </span></span></td></tr><tr class=""><td><div class="_3ad4">7 Mar '24 - 10 Mar '24</div></td><td><span class="_19b8"><span>CUET PG 2024 Admit Card</span></span></td></tr><tr class=""><td><div class="_3ad4">4 Mar '24 - 26 Mar '24</div></td><td><span class="_19b8"><span>CUET PG 2024 Advance City Intimation Slip</span></span></td></tr></tbody></table></div></div></div></div><div class="_640a"><div class="_9e70"><div class="d5f9"><div><img loading="lazy" class="_1752 _6e6d _22c3" src="./cutmhome_files/qna.svg" alt="Q&amp;A Icon"></div><div class="_5977"><h5>Commonly asked questions <div>On <!-- -->Admissions</div></h5></div></div><div id="sectional-faqs-0" class="_6e6a sectional-faqs"><p id="0::354441" class="_5543 listener" style="animation-delay:0s"><strong class="flx-box"> <span>Q: &nbsp;</span> <span>How do I get a seat at Centurion University? </span></strong></p><div class="ff6c"><div class="wikiContents"><div class="_3063"> <span> A:&nbsp; </span> <div> <p>The University conducts a common Entrance Exam for the UG &amp; PG courses. The Entrance Exam dates for the academic year 2023: <strong>30th of every month</strong> starting from <strong>30th Dec 2022 to 30<sup>th</sup> August 2023.</strong> Last date of applying will be 25 Aug 11:59 PM with a minimum fee of INR 600. To get admission in Centurion University you need to follow the mentioned below steps:</p><p>Step 1: Apply for the entrance exam CUEE- 2023, through the official website. The mode of examination will be Online/Offline.</p><p>Step 2: The registered candidates will be informed about the exam time, link, credentials, etc. via E-mail.</p><p>Step 3: Result Declaration, Reporting for Counselling and admission.</p><p>Step 4: Documentation process</p><p>Step 5: Reporting details (date, time, schedule, etc.)</p></div></div></div></div><p id="0::354443" class="_5543 listener" style="animation-delay:0s"><strong class="flx-box"> <span>Q: &nbsp;</span> <span>What is the mode of application at Centurion University Bhubaneswar? </span></strong></p><div class="ff6c"><div class="wikiContents"><div class="_3063"> <span> A:&nbsp; </span> <div> <p>The mode of application is Online &amp; Offline as well. The Entrance Exam dates for the academic year 2023: <strong>30th of every month</strong> starting from <strong>30th Dec 2022 to 30<sup>th</sup> August 2023.</strong> Last date of applying will be 25 Aug 11:59 PM with a minimum fee of INR 600. The applicants can apply from the official website of the CUTM. For the applicants who are appearing for the online mode need to give proctored based test, and for the offline applicants, should report to Notified Test Centre or at the University campus. To get admission in Centurion University you need to follow the mentioned below step:</p><p>Step 1: Apply for the entrance exam CUEE- 2023, through the official website. The mode of examination will be Online/Offline.</p><p>Step2: The registered candidates will be informed about the exam time, link, credentials, etc. via E-mail.</p><p>Step 3: Result Declaration, Reporting for Counselling and admission.</p><p>Step 4: Documentation process</p><p>Step 5: Reporting details (date, time, schedule, etc.)</p></div></div></div></div><p id="0::354447" class="_5543 listener" style="animation-delay:0s"><strong class="flx-box"> <span>Q: &nbsp;</span> <span>Does Centurion University offer Diploma courses, what is the eligibility criteria? </span></strong></p><div class="ff6c"><div class="wikiContents"><div class="_3063"> <span> A:&nbsp; </span> <div> <p>Yes, Centurion University offers Diploma courses with various programme like School of Paramedics &amp; allied Health Science, School of Pharmacy and Life Sciences and School of Vocational Training, refer to the table for more understanding.</p><table style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%;" border="1"><colgroup><col style="width: 50%;"><col style="width: 50%;"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th>Diploma Courses</th><th>Eligibility&nbsp;</th></tr><tr><td>School of Paramedics &amp; allied Health Science (8 courses)</td><td>Class 12, CUEE&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td>School of Pharmacy and Life Sciences</td><td>Class 12, CUEE&nbsp;</td></tr><tr><td>School of Vocational Training (13 courses)</td><td>Class 12, CUEE&nbsp;</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div></div></div><p id="0::449167" class="_5543 listener" style="animation-delay:0s"><strong class="flx-box"> <span>Q: &nbsp;</span> <span>Can I get direct admission to Centurion University of Technology and Management, Bhubaneswar?</span></strong></p><div class="ff6c"><div class="wikiContents"><div class="_3063"> <span> A:&nbsp; </span> <div> Admissions are purely merit based and will be provided based on the students performance in the entrance exams.Like Btech admission Centurion University need twelve result or diploma result performence.
Other branches have other types of performances</div></div></div><a class="e21b" href="https://ask.shiksha.com/can-i-get-direct-admission-to-centurion-university-of-technology-and-management-bhubaneswar-qna-7444057"> <!-- -->View Other Answers<!-- --> <i class="_6c18 d30c"></i></a></div></div></div></div><a class=" _5a11  ripple dark" href="https://www.shiksha.com/college/centurion-university-of-technology-and-management-bhubaneswar-campus-53057/admission?scrollDateWithExams=true"><div class="b952 _9857 primaryButton" role="button"><span class="d9de _9c85">Admission Details for all courses</span><img loading="lazy" class="ffdf _6e6d d337" src="./cutmhome_files/RightArrow.svg" alt="Right Arrow Icon"></div></a></div></div></section></div><div id="ovp_section_placements"><section class="_1248 boxShadow" id="ovp_section_placements"><div class="e3e7  a694 h2"><h2 class="_2b31"><div class="_6a22 ">Centurion University Bhubaneswar Placements 2024</div></h2></div><div class=""><div class="b120"><div class="wikiContents _021e collapsed ca53 _5333 a78b    _0443" style="content-visibility:auto;contain-intrinsic-size:auto 180px;--maxHeightOfBlock:180px"><div><div class="faq__according-wrapper"><div><p>The final placements for all campuses of CUTM are managed and monitored by its designated centralised Career Development Cell (CDC). CDC conducts a number of career counseling and training programmes for the students and also monitors the recruitment activities at every campus. It organises a range of programmes such as JAVA certification in association with IBM, Network Certification in association with CISCO, DB2 training Certification in association with IBM, and Campus Connect in association with Infosys for the active development of students at regular intervals.</p>
<p>The University has also signed MoUs with a number of companies such as Yamaha, Godrej, VOLVO Eicher, Hyundai Motors Pvt Ltd and Tata Automation Limited for the benefits of its students. Some of the key recruiters that have hired the students of this University during 2022 placements include the following:</p>
