ata/ugcDocuments/images/wordpressImages/2021_08_Data-scientist-salaries_480x360.jpg","altText":"Data Scientist Salaries – Your Ultimate Guide","views":22219}]}],"contextualMenu":[],"blog":{"trending":{"data":[],"viewAll":""},"popular":{"data":[],"viewAll":""},"latest":{"data":[{"title":"What is ul Tag in HTML?","link":"https://www.shiksha.com/online-courses/articles/what-is-ul-tag-in-html-blogId-146251"},{"title":"Basics of Intraday Trading for Beginners","link":"https://www.shiksha.com/online-courses/articles/basics-of-intraday-trading-blogId-149653"},{"title":"Augmented Reality vs Virtual Reality","link":"https://www.shiksha.com/online-courses/articles/augmented-reality-vs-virtual-reality/"},{"title":"Learning div Tag in HTML","link":"https://www.shiksha.com/online-courses/articles/learning-div-tag-in-html-blogId-145655"},{"title":"Types Of Hackers To Be Aware Of In 2024","link":"https://www.shiksha.com/online-courses/articles/types-of-hackers-to-be-aware-of/"}],"viewAll":""}}},"childPageData":{"status":200,"pageType":"iulp","listingName":"Centurion University of Technology and Management, Bhubaneswar Campus","abbrevation":"CUTM","listingNameWithCityLocality":"Centurion University of Technology and Management, Bhubaneswar Campus","listingId":53057,"listingType":"institute","seoUrl":"/college/centurion-university-of-technology-and-management-bhubaneswar-campus-53057","anaUrl":"/college/centurion-university-of-technology-and-management-bhubaneswar-campus-53057/questions","aboutCollege":"\u003cp>GATE 2024 exam will be conducted between \u003cstrong>Feb 3, 2024\u003c/strong> and \u003cstrong>Feb 11, 2024\u003c/strong>.\u003c/p>","anaPdfUrl":"https://images.shiksha.com/mediadata/instituteCtaPdf/questions/53057.pdf?v=1658535253","isMultipleLocation":false,"scholarshipInfo":{"scholarShipDetails":[{"listingId":53057,"description":"Eligibility Criteria for Scholarship 2022-20223\n\nA) Merit-based Scholarship for B.Tech. students (Except CSE branch):\n\n1) Odisha Board\n- 10% Scholarship offered to candidates with 60% and above marks\n-  5% Scholarship offered to candidates with 50-59% and above marks\n\n2) AP Board\n- 10% Scholarship offered to candidates with 80% and above marks\n-  5% Scholarship offered to candidates with 70-79% and above marks\n\n3) Other Board\n- 10% Scholarship offered to candidates with 70% and above marks\n-  5% Scholarship offered to candidates with 60-69% and above marks\n\nNote: Special Scholarship 5% for all CUEE applicants.","scholarship_type_id":201,"scholarship_type_name":"Scholarship"},{"listingId":53057,"description":"B) Merit-based Scholarship for Diploma (Except Paramedical)\n\n1) Odisha Board\n- 15% Scholarship offered to candidates with 60% and above marks\n- 10% Scholarship offered to candidates with 50-59% and above marks\n\n2) Other Board\n- 15% Scholarship offered to candidates with 61% and above marks\n-  10% Scholarship offered to candidates with 50-59% and above marks\n\nSecond Year Onwards the Scholarship Criteria:\n- Student need to score 8.0 CGPA in semester exams\n- The students need to have 80% attendance\n\nFor more scholarships, please visit https://cutm.ac.in/admission/scholarship/","scholarship_type_id":201,"scholarship_type_name":"Scholarship"}],"allScholarshipPageUrl":"/college/centurion-university-of-technology-and-management-bhubaneswar-campus-53057/scholarships","pdfUrl":null,"scholarshipSummaryInfo":null},"eventInfo":{"eventsDetails":[],"eventsUrl":{},"defaultUrl":"https://www.shiksha.com/pwa/public/images/default-event-image.jpg"},"media":{"photos":{"Campus View":[{"mediaId":1340271,"thumbUrl":"https://images.shiksha.com/mediadata/images/1650542961phpkgitSL_100x78.jpg","mediaUrl":"https://images.shiksha.com/mediadata/images/1650542961phpkgitSL.jpeg","widgetThumbUrl":"https://images.shiksha.com/mediadata/images/1650542961phpkgitSL_205x160.jpg","mediaTitle":"Header","altText":"Centurion University Bhubaneswar Campus View(1)"},{"mediaId":924555,"thumbUrl":"https://images.shiksha.com/mediadata/images/1581325790phpYnRqCI_100x78.jpg","mediaUrl":"https://images.shiksha.com/mediadata/images/1581325790phpYnRqCI.jpeg","widgetThumbUrl":"https://images.shiksha.com/mediadata/images/1581325790phpYnRqCI_205x160.jpg","mediaTitle":"Campus View","altText":"Centurion University Bhubaneswar Campus View(2)"},{"mediaId":903683,"thumbUrl":"https://images.shiksha.com/mediadata/images/1578031181phpKw6gMv_100x78.jpg","mediaUrl":"https://images.shiksha.com/mediadata/images/1578031181phpKw6gMv.jpeg","widgetThumbUrl":"https://images.shiksha.com/mediadata/images/1578031181phpKw6gMv_205x160.jpg","mediaTitle":"Campus View","altText":"Centurion University Bhubaneswar Campus View(3)"}],"Entrance":[{"mediaId":903679,"thumbUrl":"https://images.shiksha.com/mediadata/images/1578031133phpblrZYi_100x78.jpg","mediaUrl":"https://images.shiksha.com/mediadata/images/1578031133phpblrZYi.jpeg","widgetThumbUrl":"https://images.shiksha.com/mediadata/images/1578031133phpblrZYi_205x160.jpg","mediaTitle":"Entrance","altText":"Centurion University Bhubaneswar Entrance"}],"Labs":[{"mediaId":1144673,"thumbUrl":"https://images.shiksha.com/mediadata/images/1615437894phprG6BpS_100x78.jpg","mediaUrl":"https://images.shiksha.com/mediadata/images/1615437894phprG6BpS.jpeg","widgetThumbUrl":"https://images.shiksha.com/mediadata/images/1615437894phprG6BpS_205x160.jpg","mediaTitle":"Lab","altText":"Centurion University Bhubaneswar Labs"}],"Hostel Building":[{"mediaId":903689,"thumbUrl":"https://images.shiksha.com/mediadata/images/1578031250phpIsTiEU_100x78.jpg","mediaUrl":"https://images.shiksha.com/mediadata/images/1578031250phpIsTiEU.jpeg","widgetThumbUrl":"https://images.shiksha.com/mediadata/images/1578031250phpIsTiEU_205x160.jpg","mediaTitle":"Hostel Building","altText":"Centurion University Bhubaneswar Hostel Building"}],"Classroom":[{"mediaId":903685,"thumbUrl":"https://images.shiksha.com/mediadata/images/1578031213phpP0WZ4R_100x78.png","mediaUrl":"https://images.shiksha.com/mediadata/images/1578031213phpP0WZ4R.png","widgetThumbUrl":"https://images.shiksha.com/mediadata/images/1578031213phpP0WZ4R_205x160.png","mediaTitle":"Classroom","altText":"Centurion University Bhubaneswar Classroom"}],"Campus Building":[{"mediaId":903681,"thumbUrl":"https://images.shiksha.com/mediadata/images/1578031163phpPgJrnL_100x78.jpg","mediaUrl":"https://images.shiksha.com/mediadata/images/1578031163phpPgJrnL.jpeg","widgetThumbUrl":"https://images.shiksha.com/mediadata/images/1578031163phpPgJrnL_205x160.jpg","mediaTitle":"Campus Building","altText":"Centurion University Bhubaneswar Campus Building"}],"Playground":[{"mediaId":1144675,"thumbUrl":"https://images.shiksha.com/mediadata/images/1615437915phpZopdVi_100x78.jpg","mediaUrl":"https://images.shiksha.com/mediadata/images/1615437915phpZopdVi.jpeg","widgetThumbUrl":"https://images.shiksha.com/mediadata/images/1615437915phpZopdVi_205x160.jpg","mediaTitle":"Playground","altText":"Centurion University Bhubaneswar Playground"}]},"videos":[{"mediaId":251163,"mediaUrl":"https://www.youtube.com/v/-FTYgoPtUqQ","mediaTitle":"Centurion University Bhubaneswar","thumbUrl":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/-FTYgoPtUqQ/default.jpg","altText":"Centurion University Bhubaneswar Campus View"},{"mediaId":251165,"mediaUrl":"https://www.youtube.com/v/tYSfKVRuTC8","mediaTitle":"Campus Tour","thumbUrl":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/tYSfKVRuTC8/default.jpg","altText":"Centurion University Bhubaneswar Campus View"},{"mediaId":301883,"mediaUrl":"https://www.youtube.com/v/4MWNrGMoZGE","mediaTitle":"Student Testimonials","thumbUrl":"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/4MWNrGMoZGE/default.jpg","altText":"Centurion University Bhubaneswar Others(1)"}],"photoSections":["Campus View","Campus Building","Classroom","Entrance","Hostel Building","Labs","Playground"]},"highlightsInfo":{"highlights":[{"description":"A University Which believes in Integrating Higher Education with Skills to Produce More employable workforce","description_type":"usp","posted_on":"2023-06-14 19:12:47","updated_on":"2023-09-06 12:57:51"},{"description":"Only University having 11 + On Campus Product Manufacturing Units to give students the real time  Industry Experience","description_type":"usp","posted_on":"2023-06-14 19:12:47","updated_on":"2023-09-06 12:57:51"},{"description":"A University to offer  52 Domain Specializations in Various Areas","description_type":"usp","posted_on":"2023-06-14 19:12:47","updated_on":"2023-09-06 12:57:51"},{"description":"The Centurion University of Technology and Management has 50+ Patents in various areas","description_type":"usp","posted_on":"2023-06-14 19:12:47","updated_on":"2023-09-06 12:57:51"},{"description":"The university has 50+ Industry Sponsored Action Research Centres and Action Learning Labs","description_type":"usp","posted_on":"2023-06-14 19:12:47","updated_on":"2023-09-06 12:57:51"},{"description":"Mentorship, funding (investment), market linkage to working space, and infrastructure  support for start-up ideas through Center of Innovation and Entrepreneurship","description_type":"usp","posted_on":"2023-06-14 19:12:47","updated_on":"2023-09-06 12:57:51"},{"description":"Degrees integrated with leading companies such as Dassault Systemes and AWS leading to graduation with an industry certificate","description_type":"usp","posted_on":"2023-06-14 19:12:47","updated_on":"2023-09-06 12:57:51"},{"description":"Choice based credit system and a Unique Skills for Success program to ensure high success rate and employability","description_type":"usp","posted_on":"2023-06-14 19:12:47","updated_on":"2023-09-06 12:57:51"}],"allHighlightsPageUrl":null},"facilityInfo":[{"facilityId":1,"facilityName":"Library","otherFacilities":null,"viewFacility":false,"facilityDetail":{"facility_id":1,"description":null,"additional_info":null,"has_facility":1,"parent_facility_name":null,"facility_name":"Library","order":1,"parent_id":0,"ask_details":1,"child_facilities":null}},{"facilityId":9,"facilityName":"Cafeteria","otherFacilities":null,"viewFacility":true,"facilityDetail":{"facility_id":9,"description":"CUTM cafeteria prepares Indian, South Indian, Chinese and Tandoori Items. It consists of 70 seats and is open every day from 8:00AM-10:30 AM, 12:00PM-3:30PM and 6:45PM-10:30 PM. The menu of the restaurant consists of many categories of food items such as Soft Drinks, Snacks, Chowmin & Roll, Soup, Desserts, Appetizers, Lunch and Dinner, Thali, Rice, Dal, Veg. and Non-Veg. Curry, Paneer & Mushroom Curry, Egg and Fish Curry, Chinese etc.","additional_info":null,"has_facility":1,"parent_facility_name":null,"facility_name":"Cafeteria","order":9,"parent_id":0,"ask_details":1,"child_facilities":null}},{"facilityId":3,"facilityName":"Hostel","otherFacilities":null,"viewFacility":true,"facilityDetail":{"facility_id":3,"description":"Centurion University has 6 boys hostel and 3 girls hostel. Students staying at hostels are provided with considerable options of food, for there are many mess halls in the campus. Students can choose North Indian or South Indian menu.\nIn Campus Boys and Girls hostel facilities for 10,000+ students along with AC & Non AC Accommodation and best of class mess facility","additional_info":null,"has_facility":1,"parent_facility_name":null,"facility_name":"Hostel","order":3,"parent_id":0,"ask_details":1,"child_facilities":[{"facility_id":4,"description":null,"additional_info":[{"name":"Number of Rooms","value":305},{"name":"In-Campus Hostel","value":true}],"has_facility":1,"parent_facility_name":null,"facility_name":"Boys Hostel","order":4,"parent_id":3,"ask_details":0,"child_facilities":null},{"facility_id":5,"description":null,"additional_info":[{"name":"Number of Rooms","value":158},{"name":"In-Campus Hostel","value":true}],"has_facility":1,"parent_facility_name":null,"facility_name":"Girls Hostel","order":5,"parent_id":3,"ask_details":0,"child_facilities":null},{"facility_id":6,"description":null,"additional_info":null,"has_facility":0,"parent_facility_name":null,"facility_name":"Co-ed Hoste