 all about Centurion University Rankings 2023: Times Higher Education\r\none of India's top Impact schools is the Centurion University of Technology and Management. Numerous national and international ranking agencies have continuously recognised it as one of the best Impact institutes.","tagType":"institute"}]}},"latestArticles":[{"acronym":"","blogId":147393,"blogImageURL":"/mediadata/images/articles/1552290402phpUSZ3p7.jpeg","blogText1":null,"blogTitle":"Centurion University Bhubaneswar Rankings 2023: Business Today","countryId":2,"creationDate":"2023-12-21 09:09:37","discussionTopic":8955919,"homepageImgURL":"","lastModifiedDate":"2023-12-21 09:09:37","noIndex":0,"tags":null,"url":"/business-management-studies/articles/centurion-university-bhubaneswar-rankings-2023-business-today-blogId-147393","userId":5251129,"summary":"This article is all about Centurion University Bhubaneswar Rankings 2023: Business Today\r\none of India's top MBA schools is the Centurion University of Technology and Management, Bhubaneswar Campus. Numerous national and international ranking agencies have continuously recognised it as one of the best MBA institutes.","tagType":"institute"},{"acronym":"","blogId":147391,"blogImageURL":"/mediadata/images/articles/1552290661php4loYB3.jpeg","blogText1":null,"blogTitle":"Centurion University Rankings 2023: Times Higher Education","countryId":2,"creationDate":"2023-12-21 08:50:48","discussionTopic":8955861,"homepageImgURL":"","lastModifiedDate":"2023-12-21 08:59:58","noIndex":0,"tags":null,"url":"/business-management-studies/articles/centurion-university-rankings-2023-times-higher-education-blogId-147391","userId":5251129,"summary":"This article is all about Centurion University Rankings 2023: Times Higher Education\r\none of India's top Impact schools is the Centurion University of Technology and Management. Numerous national and international ranking agencies have continuously recognised it as one of the best Impact institutes.","tagType":"institute"}],"anaWidget":{"totalNumber":39,"listingType":"institute","questionsDetail":{"8948307":[{"answerId":8970135,"answerText":"\u003cp>Centurion University of Technology and Management, Bhubaneswar is a reputed educational institution offering a wide range of courses. The university is a top MBA college in Bhubaneshwar, Odisha. The national ranking framework ranked Centurion University Technology and Management number one for MBA. Some Popular courses from the university include B.Tech, MBBS, ME/M.Tech, B.Sc, BA, B.Com, etc.\u003c/p>\u003cp>Established in 2005, Centurion University of Technology and Management (CUTM) is a multi-sector, private university located in Odisha, India. Accredited with NAAC with ‘A’ grade, the main campus of CUTM is located at Paralakhemundi (Gajapati district). Centurion University has other campuses located in \u003cstrong>Bhubaneswar\u003c/strong> and Visakhapatnam (or Vizianagaram) along with three regional campuses located in Rayagarh, Balangir (or Bolangir) and Balasore.\u003c/p>","activityTime":"2 weeks ago","answerOwnerUserId":12359639,"questionId":8948307,"aboutMe":null,"commentCount":0,"msgCount":1,"viewCount":5,"status":"LIVE","userId":43584225,"firstname":"Nishar","lastname":"Ahmed","creationDate":"2023-12-20 20:00:16","url":"https://ask.shiksha.com/which-is-the-top-course-of-centurion-university-of-technology-and-management-bhubaneswar-campus-qna-8948307","title":"Which is the top course of Centurion University of Technology and Management, Bhubaneswar Campus? ","answerOwnerName":"Anugu Nithin Reddy","answerOwnerLevel":"Contributor-Level 8","answerOwnerImage":"","likeCount":0,"dislikeCount":0,"threadStatus":null}],"8948341":[{"answerId":8970591,"answerText":"\u003cp data-sourcepos=\"1:1-1:142\">\u003cstrong>Centurion University of Technology and Management (CUTM) Bhubaneswar does not accept OJEE (Odisha Joint Entrance Examination) scores for its MBA program\u003c/strong>. OJEE is primarily used for engineering admissions in Odisha, and CUTM doesn't consider it for its MBA selection process.\u003c/p>\u003cp data-sourcepos=\"3:1-3:116\">However, I can provide you with information about the \u003cstrong>selection process for the MBA programme at CUTM Bhubaneswar\u003c/strong>:\u003c/p>\u003cp data-sourcepos=\"5:1-5:20\">\u003cstrong>Admission Modes:\u003c/strong>\u003c/p>\u003cul data-sourcepos=\"7:1-7:103\">\u003cli data-sourcepos=\"7:1-7:103\">\u003cstrong>CUET-PG:\u003c/strong> CUTM's own entrance exam specifically designed for postgraduate programs,  including MBA. This is the primary mode of selection for MBA applicants.\u003c/li>\u003cli data-sourcepos=\"8:1-8:124\">\u003cstrong>CAT:\u003c/strong> Scores from the national-level CAT exam are also accepted for MBA admissions,  offering flexibility to applicants.\u003c/li>\u003cli data-sourcepos=\"9:1-10:0\">\u003cstrong>GMAT:\u003c/strong> While not always used,  CUTM might consider GMAT scores for international applicants or in special cases.\u003c/li>\u003c/ul>\u003cp data-sourcepos=\"11:1-11:23\">\u003cstrong>Selection Criteria:\u003c/strong>\u003c/p>\u003cul data-sourcepos=\"13:1-14:34\">\u003cli data-sourcepos=\"13:1-13:117\">\u003cstrong>Entrance Exam Score:\u003c/strong> Scores obtained in CUET-PG,  CAT,  or GMAT play a significant role in the selection process.\u003c/li>\u003cli data-sourcepos=\"14:1-14:34\">\u003cstrong>Group Discussion (GD):\u003c/strong> Shortlisted candidates from the entrance exam might be invited for a group discussion to assess communication skills,  teamwork,  and critical thinking abilities.\u003c/li>\u003cli data-sourcepos=\"15:1-16:0\">\u003cstrong>Personal Interview (PI):\u003c/strong> The final stage often involves a personal interview to evaluate the candidate's personality,  motivation,  career goals,  and overall fit with the program.\u003c/li>\u003c/ul>\u003cp data-sourcepos=\"17:1-17:31\">\u003cstrong>Minimum Score Requirements:\u003c/strong>\u003c/p>\u003cul data-sourcepos=\"19:1-21:0\">\u003cli data-sourcepos=\"19:1-19:269\">\u003cstrong>There's no publicly announced minimum score requirement for any entrance exam (CUET-PG, CAT, GMAT) for CUTM's MBA program.\u003c/strong> The cut-off scores vary year-to-year depending on various factors like the number of applicants,  seat availability,  and overall competition.\u003c/li>\u003cli data-sourcepos=\"20:1-21:0\">However,  based on past trends and reports,  a good score in CUET-PG or a percentile above 70-80 in CAT might be considered competitive for securing admission.\u003c/li>\u003c/ul>","activityTime":"2 weeks ago","answerOwnerUserId":12359639,"questionId":8948341,"aboutMe":null,"commentCount":0,"msgCount":1,"viewCount":2,"status":"LIVE","userId":43584225,"firstname":"Nishar","lastname":"Ahmed","creationDate":"2023-12-20 20:00:16","url":"https://ask.shiksha.com/what-is-the-selection-process-for-mba-and-minimum-ojee-percentile-required-at-centurion-university-of-technology-qna-8948341","title":"What is the selection process for MBA and minimum OJEE percentile required at Centurion University of Technology and Management? ","answerOwnerName":"Anugu Nithin Reddy","answerOwnerLevel":"Contributor-Level 8","answerOwnerImage":"","likeCount":0,"dislikeCount":0,"threadStatus":null}],"8948347":[{"answerId":8970649,"answerText":"\u003cp data-sourcepos=\"1:1-1:152\">No, you cannot get into the MBA programme at Centurion University of Technology and Management (CUTM), Bhubaneswar Campus, with an 88% score in OJEE (Odisha Joint Entrance Examination). Here's why:\u003c/p>\u003cul data-sourcepos=\"3:1-3:56\">\u003cli data-sourcepos=\"3:1-3:56\">\u003cstrong>OJEE is primarily for engineering admissions:\u003c/strong> OJEE is meant for selecting students for B.Tech and M.Tech programs in engineering disciplines in Odisha. CUTM's MBA programme is a separate programme with its own admission criteria and entrance exams.\u003c/li>\u003cli data-sourcepos=\"4:1-4:39\">\u003cstrong>CUTM MBA doesn't accept OJEE scores:\u003c/strong> CUET-PG (Centurion University Entrance Test) and CAT (Common Admission Test) are the primary entrance exams accepted for CUTM's MBA program. OJEE scores are not considered in the selection process.\u003c/li>\u003c/ul>\u003cp data-sourcepos=\"6:1-6:147\">Therefore, having an 88% in OJEE will not be helpful for your application to the CUTM MBA program. \u003c/p>","activityTime":"2 weeks ago","answerOwnerUserId":12359639,"questionId":8948347,"aboutMe":null,"commentCount":0,"msgCount":1,"viewCount":2,"status":"LIVE","userId":43584225,"firstname":"Nishar","lastname":"Ahmed","creationDate":"2023-12-20 20:00:16","url":"https://ask.shiksha.com/can-i-get-centurion-university-of-technology-and-management-bhubaneswar-campus-mba-with-88-in-ojee-qna-8948347","title":"Can I get Centurion University of Technology and Management, Bhubaneswar Campus, MBA with 88% in OJEE? ","answerOwnerName":"Anugu Nithin Reddy","answerOwnerLevel":"Contributor-Level 8","answerOwnerImage":"","likeCount":0,"dislikeCount":0,"threadStatus":null}],"8948351":[{"answerId":8970679,"answerText":"\u003cp data-sourcepos=\"1:1-1:178\">Centurion University of Technology and Management (CUTM), Bhubaneswar Campus, offers several scholarships for its MBA program. Here's an overview of potential top scholarship options and how to avail them:\u003c/p>\u003cp data-sourcepos=\"3:1-3:26\">\u003cstrong>Types of Scholarships:\u003c/strong>\u003c/p>\u003cul data-sourcepos=\"5:1-5:116\">\u003cli data-sourcepos=\"5:1-5:116\">\u003cstrong>Merit-based Scholarships:\u003c/strong> Some scholarships are awarded based on high academic performance in qualifying exams like CUET-PG,  CAT,  or GMAT. The specific scholarship names and amounts might not be readily available,  but achieving a high score can increase your chances of receiving scholarship support.\u003c/li>\u003cli data-sourcepos=\"6:1-6:361\">\u003cstrong>State Government Scholarships:\u003c/strong> Students might be eligible for scholarships offered by the Odisha government based on specific criteria like domicile,  caste,  economic background,  etc.. You can research relevant schemes like E-Medhabruti Scholarship by the Department of Higher Education (DHE) Odisha or PRERANA Post Matric Scholarship for SC/ST/OBC & SEBC.\u003c/li>\u003cli data-sourcepos=\"7:1-7:336\">\u003cstrong>National Scholarships:\u003c/strong> Several national scholarships like Jindal Foundation Scholarship (Sitaram Jindal),  Times of India Scholarship,  and Ministry of Human Development (DHE) New Delhi can be applicable to MBA students depending on eligibility criteria. Research these options and check your eligibility on their official websites.\u003c/li>\u003cli data-sourcepos=\"8:1-9:0\">\u003cstrong>Institutional Scholarships:\u003c/strong> CUTM might offer some specific scholarships for its own students based on achievements or financial need. Contact the university admission office or department directly to inquire about such internal scholarship opportunities.\u003c/li>\u003c/ul>\u003cp data-sourcepos=\"10:1-10:30\">\u003cstrong>How to Avail Scholarships:\u003c/strong>\u003c/p>\u003cul data-sourcepos=\"12:1-13:98\">\u003cli data-sourcepos=\"12:1-12:211\">\u003cstrong>Apply for relevant scholarships:\u003c/strong> Research and shortlist scholarships for which you meet the eligibility criteria. Most scholarships require online applications through their designated websites or portals.\u003c/li>\u003cli data-sourcepos=\"13:1-13:98\">\u003cstrong>Prepare required documents:\u003c/strong> Gather necessary documents like mark sheets,  entrance exam scorecards,  income certificates,  caste certificates (if applicable),  etc..,  as specified by the scholarship guidelines.\u003c/li>\u003cli data-sourcepos=\"14:1-14:131\">\u003cstrong>Submit your application:\u003c/strong> Submit your complete application before the deadline,  ensuring all documents are attached correctly.\u003c/li>\u003cli data-sourcepos=\"15:1-16:0\">\u003cstrong>Stay updated:\u003c/strong> Follow the scholarship providers' websites or social media channels for updates on selection processes,  award announcements,  and disbursement of scholarship funds.\u003c/li>\u003c/ul>","activityTime":"2 weeks ago","answerOwnerUserId":12359639,"questionId":8948351,"aboutMe":null,"commentCount":0,"msgCount":1,"viewCount":3,"status":"LIVE","userId":43584225,"firstname":"Nishar","lastname":"Ahmed","creationDate":"2023-12-20 20:00:16","url":"https://ask.shiksha.com/what-are-the-top-scholarships-for-mba-at-centurion-university-of-technology-and-management-bhubaneswar-campus-qna-8948351","title":"What are the top Scholarships for MBA at Centurion University of Technology and Management, Bhubaneswar Campus and how to avail them? ","answerOwnerName":"Anugu Nithin Reddy","answerOwnerLevel":"Contributor-Level 8","answerOwnerImage":"","likeCount":0,"dislikeCount":0,"threadStatus":null}],"8948353":[{"answerId":8970697,"answerText":"\u003cp>Entrance exam scores Centurion University of Technology and Management, Bhubaneswar Campus accept for admission to MBA are :\u003c/p>\u003cul>\u003cli>\u003ca title=\"OJEE\" href=\"https://www.shiksha.com/mba/ojee-exam\">OJEE\u003c/a>\u003c/li>\u003cli>\u003ca title=\"CUEE\" href=\"https://www.shiksha.com/engineering/cuee-exam\">CUEE\u003c/a>\u003c/li>\u003cli>\u003ca title=\"CUET-PG\" href=\"https://www.shiksha.com/science/cuet-pg-exam\">CUET-PG\u003c/a>\u003c/li>\u003c/ul>\u003cp>Established in 2005, Centurion University of Technology and Management (CUTM) is a multi-sector, private university located in Odisha, India. Accredited with NAAC with ‘A’ grade, the main campus of CUTM is located at Paralakhemundi (Gajapati district). Centurion University has other campuses located in \u003cstrong>Bhubaneswar\u003c/strong> and Visakhapatnam (or Vizianagaram) along with three regional campuses located in Rayagarh, Balangir (or Bolangir) and Balasore.\u003c/p>","activityTime":"2 weeks ago","answerOwnerUserId":12359639,"questionId":8948353,"aboutMe":null,"commentCount":0,"msgCount":1,"viewCount":6,"status":"LIVE","userId":43584225,"firstname":"Nishar","lastname":"Ahmed","creationDate":"2023-12-20 20:00:16","url":"https://ask.shiksha.com/what-entrance-exam-scores-does-centurion-university-of-technology-and-management-bhubaneswar-campus-accept-for-qna-8948353","title":"What entrance exam scores does Centurion University of Technology and Management, Bhubaneswar Campus accept for admission to MBA? ","answerOwnerName":"Anugu Nithin Reddy","answerOwnerLevel":"Contributor-Level 8","answerOwnerImage":"","likeCount":0,"dislikeCount":0,"threadStatus":null}]},"allQuestionURL":"/college/centurion-university-of-technology-and-management-bhubaneswar-campus-53057/questions","questionOrder":[8948353,8948351,8948347,8948341,8948307],"pageSize":5,"maxPagetoDisplay":2,"anaFaqData":null,"anaWidgetPresent":false},"collegeWidget":{"collegeWidgetData":null,"agrregateReviewsData":null},"collegeCutOffWidget":{"previewText":"\n\u003cp>\u003ca href=\"https://www.shiksha.com/mba/cat-exam\" rel=\"noopener\">CAT Result 2023\u003c/a>&nbsp;has been released. The window to download the scorecard has been made live on the official website.&nbsp;Candidates will be able to&nbsp;download it by using their login ID and username.\u003c/p>\n","cutOffUrl":"/college/centurion-university-of-technology-and-management-bhubaneswar-campus-53057/cutoff","cutoffCtaPdfUrl":"https://images.shiksha.com/mediadata/instituteCtaPdf/cutoff/cutoff_53057_1704574804.pdf?v=1704582210"},"instituteTopCardData":{"instituteName":"Centurion University of Technology and Management, Bhubaneswar Campus","h1":"Centurion University Bhubaneswar: Courses, Fees, Admission 2024, Placements, Rankings","instituteSpecificationType":"College","inlineData":{"ownership":"Private","estbYear":"2005"},"headerImageDesktop":null,"headerImageMobile":null,"headerImageDesktopNew":"https://images.shiksha.com/mediadata/images/1650542958phpdoUUHY_1280x960.jpg","headerImageMobileNew":"https://images.shiksha.com/mediadata/images/1650542961phpkgitSL_270x200.jpg","logoImageUrl":"https://images.shiksha.com/mediadata/images/1650542874phpqTvh4T.jpeg","affiliationData":null,"instituteImportantData":{"autonomous":false,"nationalImportance":false,"univeristyTypeWithSpecification":null,"ugcApproved":false,"naacAccreditation":"Grade 'A'","aiuMember":false},"parentUniversityData":{"id":53023,"name":"Centurion University of Technology and Management, Paralakhemundi","url":"/university/centurion-university-of-technology-and-management-paralakhemundi-orissa-other-53023"},"rankingData":[],"instituteDisplayName":"Centurion University Bhubaneswar","ctaPdfUrl":null,"mediaCount":12,"shortNameAbbOrFullName":"Centurion University Bhubaneswar"},"instituteToolTipData":{"university_type_state":{"name":"State University","helptext":"State University is a university that is funded and run by the State Government. Since such universities are established under State Act, they are eligible to grant degrees to the students."},"university_type_central":{"name":"Central University","helptext":"Central University is a national level university which functions under the purview of the Department of Higher Education in the Ministry of Human Resource Development  and can award degrees to the students."},"university_type_deemed":{"name":"Deemed University","helptext":"Deemed (or Deemed-to-be) University is an Institution of higher education, other than universities, working at a very high standard in specific area of study. Such institutes enjoy academic status and privileges of a university and are declared 'Deemed-to-be' by the Department of Higher Education on the advice of the UGC."},"university_type_private":{"name":"Private University","helptext":"Private University is a university established through a State/ Central Act by a sponsoring body viz. a Society, a Public Trust or a Company. Such universities may be independent of UGC control over day-to-day activities, but cannot award degrees, affiliate institutes/colleges or set up off campus centres etc. without the UGC's approval."},"naac_accreditation":{"name":"NAAC Accreditation","helptext":"The National Assessment and Accreditation Council (NAAC) is an autonomous body established by the UGC to assess and accredit institutions of higher education in the country. It grades an institution from A++ (best rating) to C. Rating D indicates that the institution is not accredited."},"affiliated_definition":{"name":"Affiliated_Definition","helptext":"Colleges can be of 2 types – Constituent colleges and Affiliated colleges. Constituent colleges are colleges which are maintained by the university itself. Affiliated colleges are educational institutions that operate independently, but also have a formal collaborative agreement with a university for the purpose of awarding the degree with some level of control or influence over its academic policies, standards or programs."},"ugc_approved":{"name":"UGC Approved","helptext":"The University Grants Commission (UGC) is a statutory body established in 1956 by the Government of India through an Act of Parliament for the coordination, determination and maintenance of standards of university education in India."},"university_status":{"name":"University Status","helptext":"University Grants Commission (UGC) - It is the apex grant giving body for institutes of higher education. It provides funds to institutes and is responsible for maintaining high standards of education in the country."},"aiu_member":{"name":"Member of AIU","helptext":"Association of Indian Universities (AIU) is an association of major universities in India set up with the aim of serving as an Inter-University Organisation; to act as a bureau of information and to facilitate communication, coordination and mutual consultation amongst universities; to help universities to maintain their autonomous character and to act as the representative of universities of India."},"university_association":{"name":"University Association","helptext":"Association of Indian Universities (AIU) - This is an inter-university organization set up as a bureau to facilitate communication between all Indian universities, provide consultation, liaise between universities and the government and to help them maintain their autonomy."},"autonomous":{"name":"Autonomous","helptext":"Autonomous Institute is one which is independent of State control over day-to-day operations and curriculum. Such an institute falls under the administrative control of the Department of Higher Education but is free from external control over its academic matters."},"nationalImportance":{"name":"National Importance","helptext":"Institute of National Importance is a status accorded by an act of Parliament, to an institution of higher education which plays a pivotal role in developing highly skilled personnel within the specified region of the country/state and discipline."}},"courseWidget":{"flagshipCourseId":282634,"allCoursesUrl":"/college/centurion-university-of-technology-and-management-bhubaneswar-campus-53057/courses","allCourses":{"191590":{"name":"B.Tech. in Computer Science and Engineering","lateral":null,"twinning":null,"executive":null,"integrated":null,"dual":null,"curriculum":null,"username":17223819,"predictorUrl":null,"recognition":[{"id":45,"name":"AICTE"}],"fees":[{"category":"general","period":"overall","fees_value":600000,"fees_unit":1,"fees_type":"total","total_includes":null,"fees_disclaimer":0,"fees_unit_name":"INR"}],"nbaAccreditation":null,"eligibility":[],"locations":{},"media":[],"partner":[],"categoryId":null,"course_id":191590,"primary_id":53057,"primary_type":"institute","primary_name":"Centurion University of Technology and Management, Bhubaneswar Campus","parent_id":53057,"parent_type":"institute","parent_name":"Centurion University of Technology and Management, Bhubaneswar Campus","offered_by_id":53057,"offered_by_name":"Centurion University of Technology and Management, Bhubaneswar Ca