le":"After 10th Diploma colleges in Bhubaneswar"},{"entityId":86,"entityType":"basecourse","url":"/engineering/colleges/m-tech-colleges-bhubaneswar","title":"M.Tech colleges in Bhubaneswar"},{"entityId":191,"entityType":"basecourse","url":"/hospitality-travel/colleges/ug-diploma-college-bhubaneswar","title":"UG Diploma colleges in Bhubaneswar"},{"entityId":101,"entityType":"basecourse","url":"/mba/colleges/mba-colleges-bhubaneswar","title":"MBA colleges in Bhubaneswar"},{"entityId":30,"entityType":"basecourse","url":"/bba/colleges/bba-colleges-bhubaneswar","title":"BBA colleges in Bhubaneswar"},{"entityId":46,"entityType":"basecourse","url":"/medicine-health-sciences/physiotherapy/colleges/b-p-th-colleges-bhubaneswar","title":"B.P.Th colleges in Bhubaneswar"},{"entityId":33,"entityType":"basecourse","url":"/it-software/colleges/bca-colleges-bhubaneswar","title":"BCA colleges in Bhubaneswar"},{"entityId":124,"entityType":"basecourse","url":"/science/colleges/ph-d-physics-colleges-bhubaneswar","title":"Ph.D. colleges in Bhubaneswar"},{"entityId":6,"entityType":"basecourse","url":"/accounting-commerce/colleges/b-com-colleges-bhubaneswar","title":"B.Com colleges in Bhubaneswar"},{"entityId":24,"entityType":"basecourse","url":"/medicine-health-sciences/colleges/b-pharma-courses-bhubaneswar","title":"B.Pharma colleges in Bhubaneswar"},{"entityId":103,"entityType":"basecourse","url":"/it-software/colleges/mca-colleges-bhubaneswar","title":"MCA colleges in Bhubaneswar"}],"seoData":{"instituteAdmissionUrl":null,"pageHeading":null,"headingName":null,"headingSuffix":null,"headingPrefix":null,"scriptedText":null,"canonicalUrl":"/college/centurion-university-of-technology-and-management-bhubaneswar-campus-53057","soCanonicalUrl":null,"metaTitle":"Centurion University Bhubaneswar: Courses, Fees, Admission 2024, Placements, Rankings","metaDescription":"Centurion University of Technology and Management, Bhubaneswar Campus offers 87 Courses across 10 Streams. Read 263 Student Reviews, 39 comments. Also Download Brochures & details on Cutoff, Placements, Fees & Admissions for various courses at Centurion University Bhubaneswar.","metaKeywords":"centurion university bhubaneswar, centurion university bhubaneswar details, centurion university bhubaneswar overview, centurion university bhubaneswar courses, centurion university bhubaneswar contact, centurion university bhubaneswar fee, centurion university bhubaneswar admissions, centurion university bhubaneswar reviews, centurion university bhubaneswar placements, centurion university bhubaneswar ranking, centurion university bhubaneswar updates","prevUrl":null,"nextUrl":null,"ampUrl":null,"bhst":null,"faqContent":"\u003cdiv id=\"faqWrapper_last\" class=\"faqWrapper manual\" contenteditable=\"false\"> \n \u003cp class=\"fQ\">\u003cstrong id=\"faq_q1\">Q. Is Centurion University Bhubaneswar a recognised university campus? \u003c/strong>\u003c/p> \n \u003cdiv id=\"faq_a1\" class=\"fA\">\n  \u003cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A. Centurion University Bhubaneswar is affiliated with CUTM Paralakhemundi, which is recognised by NAAC with ‘A’ grade. Established in 2005, Centurion University of Technology and Management (CUTM) is a multi-sector, private university located in Odisha, India. The main campus of CUTM is located at Paralakhemundi (Gajapati district). With over 600 expert instructors and over 20,000 students across the world, the University has other campuses located in \u003cstrong>Bhubaneswar\u003c/strong> and Visakhapatnam (or Vizianagaram) along with three regional campuses located in Rayagarh, Balangir (or Bolangir) and Balasore.\u003c/span>\n \u003c/div> \n \u003cp class=\"fQ\">\u003cstrong id=\"faq_q2\">Q. Which courses are offered at Centurion University Bhubaneswar? \u003c/strong>\u003c/p> \n \u003cdiv id=\"faq_a2\" class=\"fA\">\n  \u003cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A. Centurion University Bhubaneswar offers a range of diploma, UG, PG, research-level and certificate programmes offered through various departments working under it. Some of the popular courses offered this campus of CUTM include BTech, BBA, BCom, BSc, MTech, MBA and MSc among various others. Centurion University BBSR admission 2022 to all the programmes is based on scores obtained in Centurion University Entrance Exam (\u003ca>CUEE\u003c/a>) conducted by the University. Centurion University, Bhubaneswar also accepts a few nation-level entrance exam scores to provide admission in courses, including MBA, BTech, BDes, BArch and MTech. \u003c/span>\n \u003c/div> \n \u003cp class=\"fQ\">\u003cstrong id=\"faq_q3\">Q. What is admission process at Centurion University Bhubaneswar? \u003c/strong>\u003c/p> \n \u003cdiv id=\"faq_a3\" class=\"fA\">\n  \u003cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A. Candidates willing to take admission to Centurion University Bhubaneswar for all the UG and PG courses are required to have a valid score in CUEE test conducted by the University or course-specific entrance rest (accepted by the University) provided they meet with the minimum eligibility criteria set by the University. For diploma and certificate courses, however, admission is based on merit scores in the last qualifying exam.\u003c/span>\n \u003c/div> \n \u003cp class=\"fQ\">\u003cstrong id=\"faq_q4\">Q. What is CUEE stand for?\u003c/strong>\u003c/p> \n \u003cdiv id=\"faq_a4\" class=\"fA\">\n  \u003cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A. CUEE stands for Centurion University Entrance Exam. It is conducted by Centurion University (CUTM), Odisha for admissions to various undergraduate and postgraduate courses offered at the various campuses of the University. CUEE 2020 will be conducted in online mode or will be a CBT (Computer Based Test).\u003c/span>\n \u003c/div> \n \u003cp class=\"fQ\">\u003cstrong id=\"faq_q5\">Q. Does Centurion University Bhubaneswar campus offer residential facilities? \u003c/strong>\u003c/p> \n \u003cdiv id=\"faq_a5\" class=\"fA\">\n  \u003cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A. Yes, Bhubaneswar campus of Centurion University offers hostel facilities to the students. Some of the other campus facilities provided at \u003c/span>Centurion University Bhubaneswar are as follows: \n  \u003cul> \n   \u003cli>Air-conditioned classrooms\u003c/li> \n   \u003cli>A fully Wi-Fi campus\u003c/li> \n   \u003cli>Well-equipped Conference hall and Seminar hall\u003c/li> \n   \u003cli>Library\u003c/li> \n   \u003cli>Transport and Medical facilities\u003c/li> \n   \u003cli>Full-time internet connectivity\u003c/li> \n  \u003c/ul> \n \u003c/div> \n \u003cp class=\"fQ\">\u003cstrong id=\"faq_q6\">Q. Does Centurion University Bhubaneswar have any industrial collaborations? \u003c/strong>\u003c/p> \n \u003cdiv id=\"faq_a6\" class=\"fA\">\n  \u003cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A. Yes, a number of programmes such as JAVA certification in association with IBM, Network Certification in association with CISCO, DB2 training Certification in association with IBM, and Campus Connect in association with Infosys are organized for the active development of students on regular intervals.\u003c/span>\n \u003c/div> \n \u003cp class=\"fQ\">\u003cstrong id=\"faq_q7\">Q. What is the application process at Centurion University Bhubaneswar? \u003c/strong>\u003c/p> \n \u003cdiv id=\"faq_a7\" class=\"fA\">\n  \u003cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A. \u003c/span>Centurion University's admission process is conducted both online and offline. Candidates seeking admission to any of the courses, need to apply on the official website by paying an amount of INR 600 to INR 1,500. The entire application process is shown below with the help of application screenshots: \n  \u003cstrong>Step 1\u003c/strong>: Visit the official website (www.cutm.ac.in). On its homepage, register yourself by providing an email id. \n  \u003cstrong>Step 2:\u003c/strong> Fill up the application form by providing all your personal details. \n  \u003cstrong>Step 3:\u003c/strong> Complete the form by providing your educational qualifications and press submit. \n  \u003cstrong>Step 4:\u003c/strong> Pay online through net banking/ debit card/ credit card.\n \u003c/div> \n \u003cp class=\"fQ\">\u003cstrong id=\"faq_q8\">Q. How is Centurion University Bhubaneswar in terms of foreign exposure? \u003c/strong>\u003c/p> \n \u003cdiv id=\"faq_a8\" class=\"fA\">\n  \u003cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A. Centurion University Bhubaneswar has signed MoUs with a number of international institutes and universities to offer world-class education and global exposure to its students at the central level across all its campuses. Some of the Universities CUTM is having tie-ups with include, University of California, Deakin University (Australia), Plymouth University (England), Box Hill Institute (Australia) and Holmesglen Institute (Australia) among various others.\u003c/span>\n \u003c/div> \n \u003cp class=\"fQ\">\u003cstrong id=\"faq_q9\">Q. Are there any scholarships offered at Centurion University Bhubaneswar? \u003c/strong>\u003c/p> \n \u003cdiv id=\"faq_a9\" class=\"fA\">\n  \u003cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A. Centurion University of Technology and Management, Bhubaneswar offers various scholarships based on prior academic record during admission and a few scholarships based on semester-wise performance for the years to follow. \u003c/span>In addition to these, ample scholarships are offered to reserved and minority category students as listed below: \n  \u003cul> \n   \u003cli>PRERANA post-matric scholarship for SC/ST/OBC and SEBC District Welfare Office (Odisha)\u003c/li> \n   \u003cli>Minority scholarship from District Welfare Office (Odisha)\u003c/li> \n   \u003cli>National scholarship\u003c/li> \n   \u003cli>Jindal Foundation scholarship (Sitaram Jindal)\u003c/li> \n   \u003cli>Times of India scholarship\u003c/li> \n  \u003c/ul> \n \u003c/div> \n \u003cp class=\"fQ\">\u003cstrong id=\"faq_q10\">Q. How are the placements at Centurion University Bhubaneswar? \u003c/strong>\u003c/p> \n \u003cdiv id=\"faq_a10\" class=\"fA\">\n  \u003cspan style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A. CUTM has a centralised placement cell operating from the main campus. Some of the t\u003c/span>op recruiters that have visited Centurion University Bhubaneswar campus for placements include Infosys, IBM, Cognizant, IndiaMart, Accolite Digital, Paytm, LensKart, Volvo and Mindtree, among others. \n \u003c/div> \n\u003c/div>","languageTag":"en"},"anaCountString":"39","relatedCHP":[{"chpId":1385,"displayName":"BSc","url":"/bsc-chp","imageUrl":"/public/mobile5/images/CHP/scienceN.jpg","desktopImageUrl":"/public/images/CHP/scienceN.jpg","entityType":"basecourse","entityId":26},{"chpId":1353,"displayName":"B Tech (Bachelor of Technology)","url":"/b-tech-bachelor-of-technology-chp","imageUrl":"/public/mobile5/images/CHP/engineeringN.jpg","desktopImageUrl":"/public/images/CHP/engineeringN.jpg","entityType":"basecourse","entityId":10},{"chpId":1527,"displayName":"MSc (Master of Science)","url":"/msc-master-of-science-chp","imageUrl":"/public/mobile5/images/CHP/scienceN.jpg","desktopImageUrl":"/public/images/CHP/scienceN.jpg","entityType":"basecourse","entityId":100},{"chpId":1381,"displayName":"B Pharmacy","url":"/b-pharmacy-chp","imageUrl":"/public/mobile5/images/CHP/medicineN.jpg","desktopImageUrl":"/public/images/CHP/medicineNew.jpeg","entityType":"basecourse","entityId":24},{"chpId":1529,"displayName":"MBA (Masters of Business Administration)","url":"/mba-masters-of-business-administration-chp","imageUrl":"/public/mobile5/images/CHP/businessN.jpg","desktopImageUrl":"/public/images/CHP/businessN.jpg","entityType":"basecourse","entityId":101},{"chpId":1871,"displayName":"D Pharma","url":"/d-pharma-chp","imageUrl":"/public/mobile5/images/CHP/medicineN.jpg","desktopImageUrl":"/public/images/CHP/medicineNew.jpeg","entityType":"basecourse","entityId":70},{"chpId":1425,"displayName":"BPT (Bachelor of Physiotherapy)","url":"/bpt-bachelor-of-physiotherapy-chp","imageUrl":"/public/mobile5/images/CHP/